399
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,760
I can call them all here.

400
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:16,790
I don't believe you.

401
00:26:17,630 --> 00:26:18,240
I...

402
00:26:26,550 --> 00:26:27,000
Wait.

403
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,870
Come on. Sit here. Sit here.

