447
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,630
Fang Shumiao!

448
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:50,150
Li Xun. Li Xun.

449
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,550
It's me, Gao Jianhong.

450
00:29:53,110 --> 00:29:54,520
